OL,3,CMum calls for change after son died
OL,4,Cfrom choking on sensory ball
OL,6,FHe died six days later due to a lack
OL,7,Fof oxygen.
OL,9,F"It was really, really hard. I think
OL,10,Fif it was part of his condition it
OL,11,Fprobably wouldn't have been as hard,"
OL,12,Fsaid Ms Buckley.
OL,14,F"He'd gone to day centre perfectly
OL,15,Fhappy on that Wednesday morning and
OL,16,Fthen six days later, we'd lost him.
OL,17,FThat's been hard to get over."
