OL,3,CMum calls for change after son died
OL,4,Cfrom choking on sensory ball
OL,6,FMs Buckley is now campaigning to make
OL,7,Fpeople aware of the danger the balls
OL,8,Fcan bring especially as they are are
OL,9,Fused by many people with complex needs.
OL,11,FShe says they are "readily available"
OL,12,Fand "not all have warnings on them".
OL,14,FMs Buckley added: "It went to an
OL,15,Finquest and was classed as an
OL,16,Faccidental death.
OL,18,F"When I mentioned to the coroner I was
OL,19,Fdoing this campaign she thought it was
OL,20,Fa fantastic idea.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/8
