OL,3,CMum calls for change after son died
OL,4,Cfrom choking on sensory ball
OL,6,F"The balls are aimed at people with
OL,7,Fspecial needs and autism. You can buy
OL,8,Fboxes of 15 of them."
OL,10,FThe family are calling for clear
OL,11,Fwarnings to be put on the balls or a
OL,12,Fban to prevent them from being used.
OL,13,FThey say they are a high risk.
OL,15,F"The fire in my belly is to get the
OL,16,Fmessage out there and so hopefully no
OL,17,Fother family has to go through what we
OL,18,Fhave," said Ms Buckley.
