OL,3,CMum calls for change after son died
OL,4,Cfrom choking on sensory ball
OL,6,F"Louis has left a massive hole in our
OL,7,Flives. For 27 years my role was to
OL,8,Flook after Lou," said Ms Buckley.
OL,10,F"If it saves one life, if it saves two
OL,11,Flives, it's amazing to think
OL,12,Funfortunately Lou's legacy was after
OL,13,Fhe's gone, that he had to make a
OL,14,Fdifference."
